.de/lehre/vorlesungen/graphik/info/csc/COL_31.htm[16]	SVS-VISTEK CAMERAS Inc., “Digital Progressive Area Scan Camera SVCam User`s Manual Monochrome / Color Version LVDS-Version / Camera Link Version with 10/12 Bit Digitization,” Ver. 1.6, May 2003.[17]	Automated Imaging Association, “Camera Link Specifications of the Camera Link Interface Standard for Digital Cameras and Frame Grabbers,” Ver.1.1, Jan. 2004.[18]	Xilinx, Inc., “MicroBlaze Processor Reference Guide,” Ver.5.2 May 9, 2005.[19]	Xilinx, Inc., “Product selection and Package Option Matrices,” 2005.[20]	Xilinx, Inc., “Designing Custom OPB Slave Peripherals for MicroBlaze,” 2002.[21]	T. Chen, “A Study of Spatial Color Interpolation Algorithms for Single-Detector Digital Cameras,” Information System Laboratory Department of Electrical Engineering Stanford University, http://www-ise.stanford.edu/~tingchen/[22]	Xilinx, Inc., “Xilinx Logicore Adder/Subtracter V7.0,” Dec. 2003.[23]	Xilinx, Inc., “Xilinx Logicore Comparator v8.0,” April 2005.[24]	Xilinx, Inc, “DSP: Designing for Optimal Results edition1.0,” edition 1.0, April 2005.[25]	Y. Zou, Z. Zhuang and H. Chen, “HW-SW Partitioning Based on Genetic Algorithm,” Congress on Evolutionary Computation, vol. 1, June 2004, pp. 628-633.[26]	An Enhanced 32-Bit Processor Core for FPGA Integration, http://ramp.eecs.berkeley.edu/Publications/MBforRAMP2.ppt[27]	Xilinx, Inc., “Xilinx Logicore Floating-Point Operator v1.0,” April 2005.


